g_odvw_1::clip_card_2::goals[0]: Bakka taatee keetiif yookaan gaaffichaaf barbaachisaa ta'e agarsiisi.
g_odvw_1::clip_card_1::goals[0]: Yeroo taatichi waan gaaffichaan wal ilaallatu hojjetu agarsiisi
g_odvw_1::markdown_card_0::text: Hiriyaakee wajjin, gaaffiiwwan kanaa gadii keessaa tokko kan wal gaafattan filadhu *Gaazexeessummaa bilbilaa wajjin muuxannoonkee maali? * Haalli adeemsa gara bakka leenjii akkami? * Hamma ammaatti kutaan leenjicharraa ati jaallatte maalidha?
g_odvw_1::text_card_0::text: Tokkoon tokkoon keessan bilbila keessaniin, gaaffiif deebii hiriyaa keessanii wajjin geggeessaa, isa booda gaaffiif deebii innimmoo sii wajjin geggeessa.
g_odvw_1::text_card_7::text: Hin yaadda'in, muraan hundi kuusaa faayaa keessa taa'a.
g_odvw_1::text_card_8::text: Ol fe'uu yeroo xumurtu, kutaatti deebi'i.
g_odvw_1::text_card_3::text: Gaaffiif deebiikeerratti eeggannoodhaan bakka mataa kenniif.
g_odvw_1::text_card_6::text: Kaardii tokkorratti muraalee baayyee yoo waraabdeetta ta'e, maxxansuukee dura muraalee 3 filadhuu hambisii kan hafan haqi.
g_odvw_1::text_card_1::text: Akka hiriyaakee dhageessutti itti dhiyaachuukee mirkaneeffadhu.
g_odvw_1::text_card_2::text: Sagaleen dudduubaa jeequ baayyeen yoo jiraate, bakka haaraa barbaadi.
g_odvw_1::title: Hiriyaakeef gaaffiif deebii dhiyeessi
g_odvw_1::intro_card_0::headline: Hiriyaakeef gaafannoo dhiyeessi
g_odvw_1::clip_card_0::goals[0]: Yaadadhu, qaamicha gaaffii tokko gaafadhu, yoo barbaachisaa ta'e yeroo baayyee waraabuu dandeessa.
